html(lang='en')
  head
    title Aqua - A website and user system (Hapi/React/Flux)
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
    link(rel='shortcut icon', href='favicon.ico')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='public/build.css')
  body
    div.jumbotron
      h1.text-center Aqua
      h2.text-center A website and user system
      p.text-center: a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg(href='https://getaqua.herokuapp.com/')
        |Live Demo on Heroku
      ul.project-links
        li: a(href='https://github.com/jedireza/aqua/') View GitHub Project
        li Version 1.0.1
        li: a(href='https://github.com/jedireza/aqua/zipball/master') Download Aqua
      div.gh-btns
        iframe(src='http://ghbtns.com/github-btn.html?user=jedireza&repo=aqua&type=watch&count=true&size=large', allowtransparency='true', frameborder='0', scrolling='0', width='135px', height='30px')
        iframe(src='http://ghbtns.com/github-btn.html?user=jedireza&repo=aqua&type=fork&count=true&size=large', allowtransparency='true', frameborder='0', scrolling='0', width='125px', height='30px')
        iframe(src='http://ghbtns.com/github-btn.html?user=jedireza&repo=aqua&type=follow&count=false&size=large', allowtransparency='true', frameborder='0', scrolling='0', width='173px', height='30px')
    div.container.marketing
      h2.text-center The front-end pages
      p.lead Home, about, sign-up and contact us
      div.well.well-video
        div.video-container
          iframe(src='https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/4592vS31EOk?rel=0', frameborder='0', width='560', height='315')
      hr
      h2.text-center Authentication screens
      p.lead Login, forgot password and reset password
      div.well.well-video
        div.video-container
          iframe(src='https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/IvbKSzIsCWU?rel=0', frameborder='0', width='560', height='315')
      hr
      h2.text-center The account area
      p.lead Mock dashboard and account settings
      div.well.well-video
        div.video-container
          iframe(src='https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/IyQCcs79Gqk?rel=0', frameborder='0', width='560', height='315')
      hr
      h2.text-center The administration area
      p.lead Manage users, accounts, admins, admin groups, and statuses
      div.well.well-video
        div.video-container
          iframe(src='https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/XbIZ4-fNx5E?rel=0', frameborder='0', width='560', height='315')
      hr
      h2.text-center The core api
      p.lead The essential business logic, totally isolated
      div.row
        div.col-sm-4
          h3
            i.fa.fa-hand-o-right
            |  Signup
          p.
            The <code>/signup</code> endpoint makes sure the supplied username
            and email address are unique and creates new <code>User</code> and
            <code>Account</code> documents.
        div.col-sm-4
          h3
            i.fa.fa-sign-in
            |  Login
          p.
            When supplied valid credentials, the <code>/login</code> endpoint
            creates a new <code>Session</code>.  We've also included
            endpoints for resetting a forgotten password.
        div.col-sm-4
          h3
            i.fa.fa-paper-plane
            |  Email utility
          p.
            The <code>/contact</code> endpoint demonstrates the built-in email
            utility. By composing Handlebars and Markdown, personalized emails
            with HTML and text parts share one template.
      div.row
        div.col-sm-4
          h3
            i.fa.fa-user
            |  Users and roles
          p.
            <code>User</code> documents store login credentials and roles.
            Aqua ships with two roles; <code>Account</code> and
            <code>Admin</code>.
        div.col-sm-4
          h3
            i.fa.fa-users
            |  Admin groups
          p.
            Aqua also ships with an <code>Admin</code> grouping facility
            (<code>AdminGroup</code>). Think about these like departments;
            sales, support, manager, etc...
        div.col-sm-4
          h3
            i.fa.fa-key
            |  Permissions
          p.
            Permissions can be granted to an <code>AdminGroup</code> or
            individually for an <code>Admin</code>. <code>Admin</code>
            permissions will win over their group's permission.
      hr
      h2.text-center Most importantly
      p.lead What you build with Aqua is more important than Aqua
    footer
